    <values>
        <field>Explanation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">EA processes that result in a FONSI are vulnerable to challenge that the agency should have prepared a full EIS given the significance of impacts. This ground is most common when the EA covers large-scale or complex projects with significant controversy, uncertainty, or precedent-setting effects. The FONSI must clearly document why no significant impacts require EIS-level analysis.</value>
